Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.91,0:00:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to know things are finally gettin'\Nback to normal around here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.87,0:00:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to have you back, Zefron.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be back...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.76,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Sorty, I missed you like the dickens!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarfy, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.60,0:00:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've had a lot of time to think and... well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I never want to be apart from you again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.31,0:00:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you make me the happiest hat alive...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.58,0:00:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and be my magical enchanted accessory for life?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that a proposal?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sorty... you're hopeless.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.42,0:00:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Wizard god, yehehes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.23,0:00:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, you two!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.65,0:00:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I be the best man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.38,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dumbledear...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.71,0:01:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, professor Dumkbledore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.94,0:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, Harry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just stopping by to say good bye\Nbefore I went home for the summer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.60,0:01:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was very sweet of you, boy, but while you're here,\NI think I have something that belongs to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.31,0:01:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, I don't know if I can ever thank you enough.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you help save me, but you helped\Nsave the entire school and Sirius Black!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.45,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, we are cool. I mean from now on, boy:\Nyou and me, we're tight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.80,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- I knew it ever since you were a little\Nbaby and I left you with the Dursleys, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...that one day you grow up to be a\Ngreat Gryffindor just like your mom and dad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.38,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're very proud of you, where-ever they are.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dumbledore, about my parents and the Dursleys...\N- Yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.41,0:01:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How come, I had to grow up in the\Nmuggle-world where everything just kind of sucks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.46,0:01:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How come, I couldn't have grown up in the wizarding world,\Nwhere everybody is... I don't know, really cool and treats me like...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...worshiped you? Treated you like an idol? Not like a little boy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.65,0:01:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, it ain't much to grow up\Nin a world where all of this wasn't special.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.77,0:02:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's our time away from Hogwarts\Nthat makes these seven short years so precious.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.03,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like with Ron and Hermin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.02,0:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you're not gonna see them for a while now, but Harry:\NYou've got these days of summer to remind you how much you really love them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.30,0:02:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all make sense when you're older,\Nnow get out of here, little scamp!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.77,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go interview our new\Ndefense-against-the-dark-arts teacher.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it down to ah,...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.95,0:02:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilderoy Lockhart, Mad-Eye Moody\Nand some fellow named ''Squirrel''.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.20,0:02:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anybody dangerous,\Nso I think I'm gonna go with the squirrel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you next year, boy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna miss you, Dumbledore.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.39,0:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will miss you too, kid. I love you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Disaparate!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright Harry, see you next year, mate! Bye!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good summer, Seamus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace, my brother, my brother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dean, get out of here, you crazy son of a bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might like this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a picture of your mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one known before she died.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Snape!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.84,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really nice of you.\NYou really are a great guy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.71,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you'd like it, not you could have it!\NIt's going back into my pillow, where it belongs!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Snape is such a dick!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.07,0:03:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We haven't to worry about that now, Harry, because...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.85,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,well... because it's summer!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got these days of summer
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to remind us of each other...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.18,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The time we have to spend apart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,will keep us in each other's heart...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping that the good ole' days are
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.78,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,something I will dream about at night...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't matter if it's soon or later,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it's gonna be alright!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see you go,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.62,0:03:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not forever, not forever!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:04:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was, you now that\NI would never let it get me down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.54,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the part of me\Nthat makes me better, wherever I go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.50,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will try\Nnot to cry--\Nbut no one needs to say goodbye...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see you go,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.99,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not forever, not forever!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.20,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was, you now\Nthat I would never let it get me down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.07,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the part of me that\Nmakes me better, wherever I go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will try\Nnot to cry--\Nbut no one needs to say goodbye!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry can you believe that we only get seven years at Hogwarts?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's what makes it so special.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure we have to go back home for summer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But imagine how... how totally awsome going back's gonna be.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.33,0:05:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,'Til then I gotta go back to the muggle-world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.16,0:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna try and tell me that this wasn't real\Nand none of this happened, but you know what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It WAS real, and it DID happen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.48,0:05:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We've spent time here, we've made\Nfriends here and... that's a part of us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.41,0:05:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz Hogwarts is... it's bigger then any of us,\Nit's bigger then any of it's founders.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's gonna be run long after we're gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll see our kids come here one day.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing about Hogwarts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.59,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how long you're away from it...\Nwell, there's always a way back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.74,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to witches and wizards and magical beasts,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to goblins and ghosts and to magical feasts,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.48,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all that I love and it's all that I need
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at Hogwarts, Hogwarts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.64,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to spells and enchantments, potions and friends,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to Gryffindors! Hufflepuffs! Ravenclaws! Slytherins!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.46,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the place where our story begins
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,at Hogwarts, Hogwarts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry, what's it's name?"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hogwarts, Hogwarts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"I didn't hear you kids!"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hogwarts, Hogwarts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Man, I'm glad we went back!"
